<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>sẖbʿy fyk bạrtwy mnk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (sẖbʿy fyk bạrtwy mnk .. ạ̹nt ạ̹lhy wʿyny ʿlyk
 mntẓrk rạḥty fy sẖkẖṣk .. qlby wrwḥy byn ạ̹ydyk)2
 1- (lmạ ạ̉sẖbʿ mnk rạḥ ạ̉dws .. ʿly̱ ʿsl ạlʿạlm wmạ fyh
 mn sẖhwẗ wdh sẖyʾ mlmws .. lkn wʿdk hạgẖlb byh)2
 2- (ạ̹rwyny bḥbk yạ fạdyã .. wạmlạny brwḥk yạ mlyk
 ạ̹kẖfyny wạnt ạ̉ẓhr fyã .. ʿlsẖạn mjdk yrjʿ lyk)2
 3- (mntẓrk gẖyr kẖṭwạty .. ạ̉tḥwl wạbqy̱ brkạn
 ytfjr ʿmlk fy ḥyạty .. tʿml byã fy kl mkạn)2
 4- (ʿyny ʿlyk tyjy wtạkẖdny .. wạʿysẖ qdạmk ʿly̱ ṭwl
 fy ạlạ̉bdyẗ ạ̉nạ hạfḍl ạ̉gẖny .. wḍyqạty tnthy wtzwl)2</lyrics>
<author>hạny nbyl, hạny nbyl</author>
<hymn_number>426</hymn_number>
</song>